item.title: Imperial College Indian Society proudly presents the longest running student show in the country - East Meets West.
item.author: Advaith Sastry,Keerthi Muthukumar,
item.description: Currently celebrating its 27th year, East Meets West is an eclectic fusion of dance, drama, fashion and music.
